Package de.tudarmstadt.ukp.clarin.webanno.brat.display.model

Provides Model classes used to display Brat annotation objects.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Argument
    The Arguments used during arc annotation in the form of [["Arg1","p_21346"],["Arg2","p_21341"]] to denote a given arc annotation such as dependency parsing and coreference resolution
    Entity
    An Entity is a span annotation with id, type and offsets of the span annotation of the format ["p_22406","KON",[[1125,1128]]] - id of POS 22406, of type KON and start offset=1125, end offset = 1128
    EntityType
    Different attributes of an Entity used for its visualisation formats.
    Offsets
    The start and End offset positions of a span annotation as required by the Brat protocol
    Offsets.OffsetsDeserializer
    Deserialize Offsets from JSON to Java.
    OffsetsList
    List of Offsets.
    Relation
    A relation between span annotations -> an arc annotation.
    RelationType
    Type of an arc.
    Stored
    Used to return name and suffix of annotation document exports.
